Description: `cpsvote` provides an automated method for downloading, recoding, and merging selected years of the 
    Current Population Survey's 
    Voting and Registration Supplement, a large N national survey into registration, voting, and non-voting in United States 
    federal elections. The
    package provides documentation for appropriate use of sample weights to generate statistical estimates. The package 
    includes multiple vignettes
    that illustrate different applications. 
